echo "Starting backup of today's work..."
backup_file="daily_backup_$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz"

files=( *.py *.md )

if [ ${#files[@]} -eq 0 ]; then
    echo "No project files found to backup."
    exit 1
fi

tar -czvf "$backup_file" "${files[@]}"

if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
    echo "Backup created: $backup_file"
else
    echo "Backup failed."
fi
"}
